<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">3. Показатели качества услуги</span></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">3.1 Перевод соответствует исходному тексту по</span></span><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 13.5pt;">&nbsp;содержанию,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 13.5pt;">смыслу,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 13.5pt;">стилистике и&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 13.5pt;">оформлению.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">3.2 Перевод является полным и адекватным.</span></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
